  "summary": {
    "en": "A 158-piece castle fort kit for larger indoor builds, cooperative play, and imaginative STEM construction.",
    "zh": "158件城堡堡垒拼搭套装，适合更大的室内搭建、协作玩耍和想象力STEM建构。"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": [
      "The set supports larger castle frames, house structures, and open play spaces for children ages 5 and up.",
      "PP rods and connector balls keep the structure light while allowing repeated assembly and storage.",
      "Large-format builds encourage cooperation, confidence, spatial reasoning, and role-play storytelling.",
      "The item is suitable for toy retail, educational activities, gift programs, and OEM/ODM customization."
    ],
    "zh": [
      "套装支持更大的城堡框架、房屋结构和开放式游戏空间，适合5岁以上儿童。",
      "PP杆件与连接球让结构保持轻便，并支持反复拼装和收纳。",
      "大型结构有助于协作、自信表达、空间推理和角色故事游戏。",
      "产品适合玩具零售、教育活动、礼品项目和OEM/ODM定制。"
    ]
  },
